        <section name="Features">
                We worked hard to provide many useful features that you can use
                on demand. From useful small util's that help ease your day in
                daily production to full blown configuration monsters. And even if
                a feature is missing, the whole system can be plugged together
                in a lot of ways.
        </section>
        
        <section name="Performance &amp; Size">
                Albeit the extended feature list, AS3commons-logging offers a high-performing
                logging solution with up to 1000000 calls in <strong>4ms</strong> in a
                deactivated state. It also has a minimum (non-configured) size
                of <strong>2.1kB</strong> putting minimum overhead to your 
                productive application.
        </section>
        
